# Sample Environment Variables for iot-monitor

# --- MQTT Broker Configuration ---
# To connect the backend (and optionally the simulator) to an EXTERNAL MQTT broker:
# 1. Rename this file to '.env'
# 2. Uncomment the following line.
# 3. Replace 'mqtt://your-real-broker-ip-or-hostname:1883' with the actual URL.
# 4. Restart the relevant services: docker compose restart backend simulator

#MQTT_BROKER_URL=mqtt://your-real-broker-ip-or-hostname:1883


# --- Session Secret ---
# Override the default session secret here for better security.
# Uncomment and set a strong, unique secret value.
# SESSION_SECRET=replace_this_with_a_much_stronger_secret_via_dotenv

